description.en: In short, What is Jiviz ? Jivizcoin is a decentralized platform that uses the strength of blockchain innovation in engaging content creators and social media users to take full control over their content and get rewarded for their creations. Our foundation is based on a straight forward Peer-to-Peer arrangement controlled by programmable clever agreements to empower reasonable compensation for all kinds of media content and creations. Our long term vision is to develop an open and decentralized domain where everybody gets compensated for their endeavors through cryptoassets.
